ournal]] |date=24 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"69eLl\">{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/sarahkim/2020/01/30/coronavirus-racism-asian-communities/ |title=As The Coronavirus Spreads, So Does Racism\u2014Both Against And Within Asian Communities |last=Kim |first=Sarah |work=[[Forbes]] |access-date=2 February 2020 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200202205424/https://www.forbes.com/sites/sarahkim/2020/01/30/coronavirus-racism-asian-communities/ |archive-date=2 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"05O7n\">{{cite web |title=London Racially Motivated Assault due to Coronavirus |url=https://www.itv.com/news/london/2020-03-04/hunt-for-racist-coronavirus-attackers-police-release-cctv-after-oxford-street-assault/ |work=[[ITV News]] |access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"pHQ6A\">{{cite news |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/02/21/europe/ukraine-wuhan-bus-coronavirus-intl/index.html |title=Protesters attack buses carrying Wuhan evacuees in Ukraine |publisher=[[CNN.com|CNN]] |date=21 February 2020 |access-date=7 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"tnWuB\">{{cite news |title=Students from Northeast complain of racism at Kirori Mal College |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/students-from-northeast-complain-of-racism-at-kmc/articleshow/74071475.cms |access-date=21 February 2020 |work=[[The Times of India]] |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200212022513/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/students-from-northeast-complain-of-racism-at-kmc/articleshow/74071475.cms |archive-date=12 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"yz1CJ\">{{cite news |title=Chinese government condemns BJP Bengal president's comment on Coronavirus' |url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/chinese-government-condemns-bjp-bengal-presidents-comment-on-coronavirus/article31044588.ece |accessdate=16 March 2020 |work=The Hindu |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312154814/https://www.thehindu.com/n